<section class="section main ">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row" style="margin-top: -40px;">
            <article class="content col-md-12">
                <div  class="owl-carousel owl-theme">
                    <div><img src="../image/homefive.webp"/></div>
                    <div><img src="../image/homeone.webp"/></div>
                    <div><img src="../image/hometwo.webp"/></div>
                    <div><img src="../image/homethree.webp"/></div>
                </div>
            </article>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container">

        <div class="row rowmain2">
            <aside class="sidebar col-md-8">
                <hr/>
                <h2 style="color: #CEA152;">Nomination</h2>
                <hr/>
                <ol class="col-md-12" style="list-style: none; padding: unset; ">

                <% for(var i=0;i<scientistList.length;i++){ %>
                        <% if(scientistList[i].status.startsWith('Nominated')){%>
                    <li class="col-md-12" style="margin-top: 30px; padding: unset">
                            <div class="col-md-4">
                                <a href="/scientist-detail?sid=<%= scientistList[i].sid %>"><img src="<%= scientistList[i].image %>"/></a>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-8" style="margin-top: -23px">
                                <h3 style="color: #0182C9"><a href="/scientist-detail?sid=<%= scientistList[i].sid %>"><%= scientistList[i].sname %></a></h3>
                                <h4 style="color: #CEA152;">Story</h4>
                                <ul>
                                    <li>Prize motivation: <%= scientistList[i].rname %></li>
                                    <br/>
                                    <li><%= scientistList[i].story %></li>
                                    <li><a href="/scientist-detail?sid=<%= scientistList[i].sid %>">More</a></li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                    </li>
                            <%};%>
                    <%};%>
                </ol>
            </aside>
            <article class="content col-md-4 rowmain1">

                <div ><img style="border-radius: 20px; margin-top: 22px" src="../image/homeeight.jpg"/></div>
                <hr/>
                <h1>Alfred Nobel’s life</h1>
                <hr/>
                <p>Alfred Nobel (1833-1896) was born in Stockholm, Sweden, on 21 October 1833. His family was descended from Olof Rudbeck, the best-known technical genius in Sweden in the 17th century, an era in which Sweden was a great power in northern Europe. Nobel was fluent in several languages, and wrote poetry and drama. Nobel was also very interested in social and peace-related issues, and held views that were considered radical during his time. Alfred Nobel’s interests are reflected in the prize he established. Learn more about his life and his interests – science, inventions, entrepreneurship, literature and peace work.</p>
                <hr/>
                <h1>Alfred Nobel’s will</h1>
                <hr/>
                <p>On November 27, 1895, Alfred Nobel signed his third and last will at the Swedish-Norwegian Club in Paris. When it was opened and read after his death, the will caused a lot of controversy both in Sweden and internationally, as Nobel had left much of his wealth for the establishment of a prize. His family opposed the establishment of the Nobel Prize, and the prize awarders he named refused to do what he had requested in his will. It was five years before the first Nobel Prize could be awarded in 1901.</p>
                <hr/>
                <h1>The establishment of the Nobel Prize</h1>
                <hr/>
                <p>In this excerpt of the will, Alfred Nobel dictates that his entire remaining estate should be used to endow “prizes to those who, during the preceding year, have conferred the greatest benefit to humankind”</p>
                <a href="/Alfred_Nobel">More</a>

            </article>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <hr/>
            <div><img src="../image/homenine.jpg"/></div>
            <p style="color: #FFFFFF; margin-top: -90px" id="descriptionimg">Featured laureates</p>

        </div>
        <div class="row rowmain2">
            <hr/>
            <div class="col-md-12">
                <ol class="col-md-12" style="list-style: none;padding: unset">
                    <% for(var i=0;i<scientistList.length;i++){ %>
                        <% if(scientistList[i].sname.includes('Albert Einstein')||scientistList[i].sname.includes('Abhijit Banerjee')||scientistList[i].sname.includes('Morgan')||scientistList[i].sname.includes('Pierre Curie')){%>
                            <li class="col-md-12" style="margin-top: 30px; padding: unset">
                                <div class="col-md-3">
                                    <a href="/scientist-detail?sid=<%= scientistList[i].sid %>"><img src="<%= scientistList[i].image %>"/></a>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-md-9" style="margin-top: -23px">
                                    <h3 style="color: #0182C9"><a href="/scientist-detail?sid=<%= scientistList[i].sid %>"><%= scientistList[i].sname %></a></h3>
                                    <h4 style="color: #CEA152;">Story</h4>
                                    <ul>
                                        <li>Nationality: <%= scientistList[i].snationality %></li>
                                        <br/>
                                        <li>Prize motivation: <%= scientistList[i].rname %></li>
                                        <br/>
                                        <li><%= scientistList[i].story %></li>
                                        <li><a href="/scientist-detail?sid=<%= scientistList[i].sid %>">More</a></li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                            </li>
                        <%};%>
                    <%};%>
                </ol>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <hr/>
                    <div><img src="../image/hometen.webp"/></div>
                    <p style="color: #FFFFFF; margin-top: -90px" id="descriptionimg">Featured research</p>
                    <hr/>

                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-12">
                        <ol>
                            <% for(var i=0;i<researchList.length;i++){ %>
                                <% if(researchList[i].rstatus.includes('Featured')){%>
                                    <li class="col-md-3" style="margin-top: 20px;height: 120px;">
                                        <h4 style="color: #0182C9; font-size: 15px; padding-right: 5px"><a href="/researchdetail?rid=<%= researchList[i].rid %>" ><%= researchList[i].rname%></a></h4>
                                    </li>
                                <%};%>
                            <%};%>
                        </ol>

                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <hr/>
            <div><img src="../image/homeeleven.jpg"/></div>
            <p style="color: #FFFFFF; margin-top: -90px" id="descriptionimg">Recent laureates</p>
            <hr/>

        </div>
        <div class="row rowmain2">
        <div class="col-md-12">
            <ol class="col-md-12">
                <% for(var i=0;i<scientistList.length;i++){ %>
                    <% if(scientistList[i].year >= 2012&&scientistList[i].status.includes('Won')){%>
                        <li class="col-md-4" style="margin-top: 30px; list-style: none; padding: unset; line-height: 2;height: 255px;">
                            <div class="col-md-6">
                                <a href="/scientist-detail?sid=<%= scientistList[i].sid %>"><img src="<%= scientistList[i].image %>"/></a>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-6">
                                <h4 style="color: #0182C9;margin-top: -3px"><a href="/scientist-detail?sid=<%= scientistList[i].sid %>"><%= scientistList[i].sname %></a></h4>
                                <ul>
                                    <li style="text-align: left;">Nationality: <%= scientistList[i].snationality %></li>
                                    <li>Born: <%= scientistList[i].birthday %></li>
                                    <li>Award Year: <%= scientistList[i].year %></li>
                                    <li><a href="/scientist-detail?sid=<%= scientistList[i].sid %>">More</a></li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                    <%};%>
                <%}%>

            </ol>

        </div>
